WEBVTT

NOTE: Estimated from known TTS script; timing requires human review before Tier 1 captions.

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:10.944
If you need to sell your house fast in Madison, Wisconsin, USA Home Buyers can give you a direct as-is option without repairs, showings, or agent commissions.

2
00:00:10.944 --> 00:00:19.457
We buy homes across Madison and Dane County, including Marquette and Willy Street, Tenney-Lapham, Vilas, South Madison, Capitol-area neighborhoods, and Dudgeon-Monroe.

3
00:00:19.457 --> 00:00:25.132
Madison can be a strong market, but not every house is easy to list.

4
00:00:25.132 --> 00:00:38.508
You may have inherited an older home, be dealing with a student rental, have tenants in place, need to sell during probate, or simply want to avoid months of repairs and open houses.

5
00:00:38.508 --> 00:00:47.021
You do not have to clean out every room, update old systems, or make the property retail-perfect before we can talk.

6
00:00:47.021 --> 00:00:49.521
The process is simple.

7
00:00:49.521 --> 00:00:53.574
Tell us about the house, the condition, and your timeline.

8
00:00:53.574 --> 00:00:59.249
We review the property, answer your questions, and give you a written cash offer.

9
00:00:59.249 --> 00:01:02.492
If it works, you choose the closing date.

10
00:01:02.492 --> 00:01:06.951
If you need more time, we can talk through that too.

11
00:01:06.951 --> 00:01:09.788
There is no obligation and no pressure.

12
00:01:09.788 --> 00:01:19.922
Our job is to explain the offer clearly so you know what happens next, what costs are avoided, and whether an as-is sale makes sense.

13
00:01:19.922 --> 00:01:26.002
For a practical cash-sale option on a Madison-area home, call USA Home Buyers at 888-274-5006.

14
00:01:26.002 --> 00:01:28.367
We will walk you through the next step.
